The tribe of Levi a poem. Tutchin, John, 1661?-1707. Dryden, John, 1631-1700.
[4], 18 p.
[s.n.], London : 1691.
A satire on the clergy. Written by John Tutchin. Cf. Halkett & Laing (2nd ed.). Has also been erroneously attributed to Dryden. First ed. Cf. BM. Reproduction of original in Harvard University Libraries.
